### ============================================
### CivicLens API Test Collection
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = {{loginResponse.response.body.token}}


### ─── 1. Health Check ────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###


### ─── 2. Admin Login ─────────────────────────

# @name loginResponse
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin@gov",
  "password": "admin@gov"
}

###


### ─── 3. Verify Auth Token ──────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


### ─── 4. Submit Ticket (with photoUrl) ──────

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Large pothole near City Mall signal causing traffic slowdown.",
  "photoUrl": "https://example.com/issues/pothole-test.jpg",
  "longitude": 77.5946,
  "latitude": 12.9716
}

###


### ─── 5. Submit Ticket (multipart with photo file) ──

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Garbage overflow near community park entrance
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="longitude"

72.8777
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="latitude"

19.076
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="test-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------FormBoundary--

###


### ─── 6. Get All Tickets (default) ──────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets

###


### ─── 7. Get Tickets — Filtered & Sorted ────

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets?status=open&category=pothole&sort=severity&page=1&limit=10

###


### ─── 8. Get Tickets — Page 2 ───────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets?page=2&limit=5

###


### ─── 9. Get Single Ticket by ID ────────────
### Replace "1" with an actual ticket ID from the GET response

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1

###


### ─── 10. Update Ticket Status ──────────────
### Replace "1" with an actual ticket ID

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}

###


### ─── 11. Update Ticket to Resolved ─────────

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "resolved"
}

###


### ─── 12. Dashboard Stats ───────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats

###


### ─── 13. Azure Blob Connectivity Test ──────

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test-azure

###


### ─── VALIDATION TESTS ──────────────────────

### ─── 14. POST Ticket — Missing required fields (expect 400)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Missing photo and coords"
}

###


### ─── 15. PATCH Ticket — Invalid status (expect 400)

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "invalid_status"
}

###


### ─── 16. GET Ticket — Non-existent ID (expect 404)

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/nonexistent999

###
